ion with other agents that are potentially hepatotoxic (e.', 'Moderate', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/12546/', '', 'Lamivudine, Paritaprevir, Glecaprevir, Tenofovir alafenamide, Maraviroc, Amprenavir, Simeprevir, Valaciclovir, Zanamivir, Cabotegravir, Lenacapavir, More', 'Hydroxocobalamin, Fomepizole, Ipecac, Nitrous acid, Dexrazoxane, Oxygen, Lanthanum carbonate, Difelikefalin, Deferoxamine, Levoleucovorin, Arginine, More', 1767369485);
